check common errors
===================

The first release will check for
missing dependencies in the META6.json file.

note App::Mi6 will not recognize a new module with
"mi6 build" if it hasn't neen added to the Git repo

bad line endings:
   |"";"| # bad
   |"";|  # good
   |"";'| # bad
   |"";|  # good

bad module names:
   |X;| # bad
   |unit module X;| # good
   |unit class X;| # good
